.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-CAPACITY-RANGE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-capacity-range \- FEAT-2803 range of per-peer total capacity
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-capacity-range
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes range of per-peer total capacity for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2803).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBpeer_capacity_range_msat\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
